OL,3,CI would not take my son to an Old Firm
OL,4,Cgame, says Swinney after latest
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FScotland's First Minister has said he
OL,8,Fwould not take his teenage son to an
OL,9,FOld Firm game, following clashes
OL,10,Fbetween fans last weekend.
OL,12,FA number of arrests have been made
OL,13,Ffollowing the scenes between Rangers
OL,14,Fand Celtic fans at the game last
OL,15,FSunday at Ibrox, which saw supporters
OL,16,Fof both clubs storm the pitch
OL,17,Ffollowing the conclusion of the
OL,18,FScottish Cup quarter-final, and
OL,19,Fstewards and police attacked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
