OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773450175
OL,3,CI would not take my son to an Old Firm
OL,4,Cgame, says Swinney after latest
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FSpeaking to the Press Association this
OL,8,Fweek, John Swinney said the actions of
OL,9,Fthe fans involved were "completely and
OL,10,Futterly unacceptable".
OL,12,F"The risk to other fans, to members of
OL,13,Fthe stewarding staff, to police
OL,14,Fofficers, to players, was just
OL,15,Fterrible," he said.
OL,17,FAsked if he would take his teenage son
OL,18,FMatthew to an Old Firm game, the First
OL,19,FMinister said: "No."
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@UO]tD@AOUwD@JO]{D@POU{D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
