CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773450175
OL,3,CI would not take my son to an Old Firm
OL,4,Cgame, says Swinney after latest
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FBut he stopped short of suggesting
OL,8,Ffuture Old Firm games should be played
OL,9,Fbehind closed doors, without
OL,10,Fsupporters in attendance.
OL,12,F"I would rather that's not the case,
OL,13,Fbut I think none of us can watch those
OL,14,Fscenes and think that there isn't
OL,15,Fsomething that's got to give as a
OL,16,Fconsequence of what happened at the
OL,17,Fweekend," he said.
OL,19,F"I want to take time to engage... the
OL,20,Fclubs and the SFA, to identify what's
OL,21,Fthe best course of action to take."
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@IO]{D@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
