OL,3,CI would not take my son to an Old Firm
OL,4,Cgame, says Swinney after latest
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FClashes have flared in recent years
OL,8,Fwhen the two teams have faced each
OL,9,Fother, including in the 2024 League
OL,10,FCup final when police were forced to
OL,11,Fuse special powers to lower the bar
OL,12,Ffor searches to take place following
OL,13,Freports of missiles being thrown at
OL,14,Fofficers and the windows of a city
OL,15,Fcentre pub being smashed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
