PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773450175
OL,3,CI would not take my son to an Old Firm
OL,4,Cgame, says Swinney after latest
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,FMr Swinney said the way to stop the
OL,8,Fviolence between the two fanbases is
OL,9,Ffor the clubs to engage with
OL,10,Ffootballing authorities, police and
OL,11,Fthe Government, adding he will be
OL,12,Flooking at the use of banning orders
OL,13,Fif he is re-elected as First Minister
OL,14,Fin May.
OL,16,F"The way through this, I think, is
OL,17,Fit's got to involve, first of all, the
OL,18,Fpeople responsible being apprehended,
OL,19,Fand the police are pursuing that," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773450175
OL,3,CI would not take my son to an Old Firm
OL,4,Cgame, says Swinney after latest
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,F"I welcome what Police Scotland are
OL,8,Fdoing.
OL,10,F"There's also got to be engagement
OL,11,Fbetween the clubs, the Scottish
OL,12,FFootball Association and the
OL,13,FGovernment about what further steps
OL,14,Fcan be taken to avoid a recurrence of
OL,15,Fthis behaviour, because it is just
OL,16,Fquite simply intolerable that we have
OL,17,Fthat now.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
