PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773450175
OL,3,CI would not take my son to an Old Firm
OL,4,Cgame, says Swinney after latest
OL,5,Cdisorder
OL,7,F"We've just concluded a consultation
OL,8,Fon football banning orders ` we have
OL,9,Ffootball banning orders available
OL,10,Falready, we've got to review them
OL,11,Fperiodically to see if they remain
OL,12,Fappropriate for the times.
OL,14,F"We're analysing the outcome of that
OL,15,Fand there's been a big response to
OL,16,Fthat and we need to do that carefully,
OL,17,Fthen in the next Parliament, we'll
OL,18,Fhave to look at these issues."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@^O]
